data.description: Lovely and well cared for home in a wonderful 55 + gated community of Desert Willows.  2-Bedrooms and two baths.  Two car tandem garage.  Home is freshly painted, newer wood-type laminate floors.  Large eat-in kitchen with tons of cabinets and drawers. Newer a/c System,Low HOA fabulous Clubhouse and pool/spa area.    Its a great community and a wonderful home!!  We think you will LOVE it.
